These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, malaysian, argentine, spanish
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, bongani, bolivar, baccarat
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, lawyer, project-manager, entrepreneur
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, lilac, pink, ebony
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, jazz, rock
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, helicopter, car
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, sailing, volleyball, weightlifting
 1. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
 2. the person who likes lilac is the bongani-smoker##1
 3. the baccarat-smoker is the person driving the motorbike##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is the bongani-smoker##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is rowing and the project-manager##2
 6. the fisherman is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
 7. the italian is the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the italian is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who likes pink is the malaysian##1
10. the argentine is in an even position##4
11. the spanish is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
12. the italian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
13. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the fan of rock##1
14. the baccarat-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person who likes yellow is on the far left##1
16. the spanish is in an odd position##4
17. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
18. the person driving the car is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
19. the fan of folk is the siglo-smoker##1
20. the fan of jazz is on the left of the lawyer##1
21. the person who likes lilac is the bongani-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Nationality      | spanish        | argentine   | italian         | malaysian  |
| Cigar          | bolivar         | bongani   | siglo   | baccarat |
| Job         | project-manager | lawyer    | entrepreneur | fisherman   |
| Color   | yellow        | lilac  | ebony      | pink   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz          | rock       | folk        | ambient   |
| Transport           | car        | helicopter      | airplane    | motorbike    |
| Sport         | weightlifting | volleyball | rowing      | sailing   |

