 9. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3
10. the chef is on the far right##1
11. the chef is the italian##1
12. the dutch is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
13. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3
14. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the chef##1
15. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
16. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
