 7. the person driving the boat is the mechanic##1
 8. the person who likes lavender is on the far right##1
 9. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
10. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
11. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the fan of techno##3
12. the fan of trance is the person driving the airplane##1
13. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4
14. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the security-guard##1
15. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
16. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
17. the person who's birthday is in may is the person who's sport is basketball##1
18. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
19. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the mechanic##3

