There 4 different types of food: asparagus, cherry, peas, pineapple
City: hamburg, liverpool, colone, prague
House: ranch-style, craftsman, farmhouse, cape-cod
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, paramedic, mechanic, musician
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, card-games, writing, hiking
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, march, november, may
 1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 2. the person traveling to colone is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 4. the paramedic is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 5. the architect is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person eating peas##1
 7. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 8. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
10. the person drinking coffee is the ranch-style house##1
11. the person traveling to liverpool is the person drinking water##1
12. the person drinking lemonade is between the person eating peas and the person drinking coffee##2
13. the architect is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
14. the ranch-style house is the person traveling to colone##1
15. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person eating pineapple and the musician##2
16. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left or far right##3
17. the person traveling to hamburg is in an odd position##4
18. the person traveling to liverpool is the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |     4      |
